parameters: There's a dungeon even in a place like this?

Elena I understand that Masamune doesn't have a
girlfriend, but does Amelia really not have one
either?
Amelia Yeah, I don't have one.
Masamune (What do you mean by 'I understand'?)
Elena What? Do you have a complaint?

Elena Yeah, that's right. Masamune doesn't seem
to have had a girlfriend before.
Masamune No, that's a lie. I've never had one.

Elena Why don't you stop putting on a boring
facade?

Masamune (Even though it's true... I can't say
that the person is Amelia from the past)

Elena But if that's the case... Elena can be a
candidate for girlfriend, right?
Amelia W-What are you saying, Elena-chan!

Elena It's not a big deal. Masamune is free,
after all.

Amelia But it's too sudden! And do you really
like me?

Elena I mean, it might be interesting to try
dating a virgin.
Masamune Well... I'm a virgin though.
Elena Hey, what do you think, Masamune?

Elena I actually have quite a big chest... Wanna
touch it?
Elena You can keep squeezing them.
Amelia No! Stay away, both of you.

Amelia It's not good to do that without being in
a relationship.
Elena We should just start dating from now on.

Masamune No... It's unreasonable to want to date
someone just because they're a virgin.

Elena But... if it's because you've genuinely
fallen in love, will you consider it?

Elena No way, there's no chance Elena would ever
like Masamune.

Masamune Enough with the idle chatter. Let's
move forward quickly.
